data.description: $5,000 use as you choose credit with an accepted offer has been added to this nearly new home. You will love the openness of this split floorplan. Two large bedrooms with walk-in closets on one side of the home, and a huge primary suite on the opposite side of the home. The open galley style kitchen has a large island/snack bar, with plenty of storage and stainless-steel appliances. Being just over a year since the home was installed, the owners did not have the time to start their landscaping plans, leaving this lot a blank canvas. The neighborhood is conveniently located between Camp Lejeune/Jacksonville and the historic waterfront of Swansboro, our ''Friendly City by the Sea''.  Enjoy the beach? This beautiful home is a short 20-minute drive to the stunning beaches of vacation destination, Emerald Isle. With transferable home warranty (expires 2027).
